# The `SampleProfileMap` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

## Description {#details}

This class provides operator overloads to the map container using <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/md5">MD5</a> as the key type, so that existing code can still work in most cases using <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sampleprof/samplecontext">SampleContext</a> as key.

Note: when populating container, make sure to assign the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sampleprof/samplecontext">SampleContext</a> to the mapped value immediately because the key no longer holds it.
